data.description: Come check out this home in Encino Mesa! It's on a quiet cul-de-sac and is within walking distance of both an Elementary and Middle school. The open floor plan makes it great for everyday living, and it's conveniently close to highways 281 and 1604, as well as libraries, shopping, and restaurants. Don't miss this opportunity to see it for yourself!
